name: Champs-Elysees
description:
The Champs-Elysees, perhaps the most famous road for any sprinter, certainly the most coveted victory you could have as a sprinter. Winning the final stage of the Tour de France, in Paris, on this famous 1.9Km section of cobbled avenue. As we head into the preparation phase of this Sprint Focussed Programme, we simulate the final stage of the Tour de france, with a series of hard efforts, culminating in a sprint for the win!
